metadata.description:
Ethereal Unreal 
By Duane Toops of Duanetoops.com and theunusualbuddha.com. This piece is a blackout poem created from a page of The Practical Meditation Journal by Jim Martin.
Duane is writer, poet, and maker who celebrates his spirituality through art and creativity. This blossoming creator seeks to bring something simplistic and endearing to fans of his work and those who cast a glance
Enjoy
